    "date": "2021-04-05T13:08:02Z",
    "text": "Reservist Pay Equity Act of 2021\n\nThis bill increases the rate of the differential wage payment tax credit from 20% to 50% and requires that the maximum dollar amount of such credit be adjusted for inflation after 2021. The credit is allowed to employers for their employees who are active duty members of the uniformed services."
